  <scopecontent id="aspace_ad515b78cbbe3e518860c1be461017e4">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Minutes of annual conventions of the Chautauqua County Republican Party, with a history of the party in Chautauqua County.</p><p> Minutes that do not contain the names of the chairman and secretaries are marked with an asterisk.</p>  </scopecontent>
